quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  41,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  41,1,h m
  41,2,yeh khuday-e Rehman o Raheem ki taraf se nazil kardah cheez hai
  41,3,"aik aisi kitaab jis ki ayaat khoob khol kar bayan ki gayi hain, arabi zabaan ka quran, unn logon ke liye jo ilm rakhtay hain"
  41,4,basharat dainay wala aur dara dainay wala magar inn logon mein se aksar ne is se ro gardani ki aur woh sun kar nahi dete
  41,5,"kehte hain"" jis cheez ki taraf to hamein bulaa raha hai is ke liye hamaray dilon par ghilaaf charrhey hue hain, hamaray kaan behray ho gay hain, aur hamaray aur tairay darmain aik hijaab haail ho gaya hai to apna kaam kar, hum apna kaam kiye jayen ge """
  41,6,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho, mein to aik bashar hon tum jaissa mujhe wahi ke zareya se bataya jata hai ke tumhara khuda to bas aik hi khuda hai, lehaza tum seedhay usi ka rukh ikhtiyar karo aur is se maffi chaho tabahi hai unn mushrikon ke liye"
  41,7,jo zkoh nahi dete aur akhirat ke munkir hain
  41,8,"rahay woh log jinhon ne maan liya aur naik aamaal kiye, unn ke liye yaqeenan aisa ajar hai jis ka silsila kabhi totnay wala nahi hai"
  41,9,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! inn se kaho, kya tum uss khuda se kufar karte ho aur dosaron ko uss ka humsartehraتے ho jis ne zameen ko do dinon mein bana diya? wohi to saaray Jahan walon ka rab hai"
  41,10,uss ne ( zameen ko wujood mein laane ke baad ) oopar se is par pahar jama diye aur is mein barkaten rakh den aur is ke andar sab mangnay walon ke liye har aik ki talab o haajat ke mutabiq theek andazay se khoraak ka samaan muhayya kar diya yeh sab kaam chaar din mein ho gay
  41,11,"phir woh aasman ki taraf mutwajjah howa jo uss waqt mehez dhuwan tha uss ne aasman aur zameen se kaha"" wujood mein aa jao, khuwa tum chaho ya nah chaho"" dono ne kaha"" hum aa gay farmabardaron ki terhan """
  41,12,"tab uss ne do din ke andar saat aasman bana diye, aur har aasman mein uss ka qanoon wahi kar diya aur aasman duniya ko hum ne charaghoon se aaraasta kya aur usay khoob mehfooz kar diya yeh sab kuch aik zabardast Aleem hasti ka mansoobah hai"
  41,13,ab agar yeh log mun morty hain to inn se keh do ke mein tum ko usi terhan ke aik achanak toot parney walay azaab se darata hon jaissa Aad aur smod par nazil howa tha
  41,14,"jab khuda ke rasool unn ke paas agay aur peechay, har taraf se aeye aur inhen samjhaya ke Allah ke siwa kisi ki bandagi nah karo to unhon ne kaha"" hamara rab chahta to farishtay bhejta, lehaza hum uss baat ko nahi mantay jis ke liye tum beje gay ho """
  41,15,"Aad ka haal yeh tha ke woh zameen mein kisi haq ke baghair barray ban baithy aur kehnay lagey"" kon hai hum se ziyada zor aawar"" unn ko yeh nah soojha ke jis khuda ne un ko peda kya hai woh un se ziyada zor aawar hai? woh hamari ayaat ka inkaar hi karte rahay"
  41,16,"aakhir kaar hum ne chand manhoos dinon mein sakht tofani howa un par bhaij di taakay inhen duniya hi ki zindagi mein zillat o ruswai ke azaab ka maza chakkha den, aur akhirat ka azaab to is se bhi ziyada ruswa kin hai, wahan koi un ki madad karne wala nah ho ga"
  41,17,"rahay smod, to un ke samnay hum ne raah raast paish ki magar unhon ne rasta dekhnay ke bajaye andha bana rehna pasand kya aakhir unn ke krtoton ki badolat zillat ka azaab unn par toot para"
  41,18,aur hum ne unn logon ko bacha liya jo imaan laaye thay aur gumraahi o bad amli se parhaiz karte thay
  41,19,aur zara uss waqt ka khayaal karo jab Allah ke yeh dushman dozakh ki taraf jaane ke liye ghair laaye jayen ge unn ke uglo ko pichlon ke anay taq rok rakha jaye ga
  41,20,phir jab sab wahan poanch jayen ge to un ke kaan aur un ki ankhen aur un ke jism ki khalin un par gawahi den gi ke woh duniya mein kya kuch karte rahay hain
  41,21,"woh apne jism ki khaalon se kahin ge"" tum ne hamaray khilaaf kyun gawahi di ?"" woh jawab den gi"" hamein usi khuda ne goyai di hai jis ne har cheez ko goya kar diya hai usi ne tum ko pehli martaba peda kya tha aur ab usi ki taraf tum wapas laaye ja rahay ho"
  41,22,tum duniya mein juraim karte waqt jab chaptay thay to tumhe yeh khayaal nah tha ke kabhi tumahray apne kaan aur tumhari ankhen aur tumahray jism ki khalin tum par gawahi den gi balkay tum ne to yeh samgha tha ke tumahray bohat se aamaal ki Allah ko bhi khabar nahi hai
  41,23,"tumhara yahi gumaan jo tum ne apne rab ke sath kya tha, tumhe le dooba aur isi ki badolat tum khasaray mein par gay """
  41,24,"is haalat mein woh sabr karen ( ya nah karen ) aag hi un ka thikana ho gi, aur agar rujoo ka mauqa chahain ge to koi mauqa inhen nah diya jaye ga"
  41,25,"hum ne un par aisay saathi musallat kar diye thay jo inhen agay aur peechay har cheez khushnuma bana kar dikhata thay, aakhir-kaar unn par bhi wohi faisla azaab chaspan ho kar raha jo un se pehlay guzray hue junoo aur insanon ke garohoon par chaspan ho chuka tha, yaqeenan woh khasaray mein reh jaane walay thay"
  41,26,"yeh munkareen haq kehte hain"" iss quran ko hargiz nah suno aur jab yeh sunaya jaye to is mein khlal daalo, shayad ke is terhan tum ghalib aa jao """
  41,27,inn kafiroon ko hum sakht azaab ka maza chakkha kar rahen ge aur jo bad tareen harkaat yeh karte rahay hain un ka poora poora badla aِnhin den ge
  41,28,woh dozakh hai jo Allah ke dushmanon ko badlay mein miley gi usi mein hamesha hamesha ke liye inn ka ghar ho ga yeh hai saza iss jurm ki ke woh hamari ayaat ka inkaar karte rahay
  41,29,"wahan yeh kafir kahin ge ke"" ae hamaray rab, zara hamein dikha day unn junoo aur insanon ko jinhon ne hamein gumraah kya tha, hum inhen paon taley roond dalain ge taakay woh khoob zaleel o khawar hon """
  41,30,"jin logon ne kaha ke Allah hamara rab hai aur phir woh is par saabit qadam rahay, yaqeenan unn par farishtay nazil hotay hain aur un se kehte hain ke"" nah daro, nah gham karo, aur khush ho jao uss jannat ki basharat se jis ka tum se wada kya gaya hai"
  41,31,"hum iss duniya ki zindagi mein bhi tumahray saathi hain aur akhirat mein bhi, wahan jo kuch tum chaho ge tumhe miley ga aur har cheez jis ki tum tamanna karo ge woh tumhari hogi"
  41,32,"yeh hai samaan ziyafat uss hasti ki taraf se jo ghafoor aur Raheem hai """
  41,33,aur uss shakhs ki baat se achi baat aur kis ki ho gi jis ne Allah ki taraf bulaya aur naik amal kya aur kaha ke mein musalman hon
  41,34,"aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, neki aur badi yaksaa nahi hain tum badi ko uss neki se dafaa karo jo behtareen ho tum dekho ge ke tumahray sath jis ki adawat pari hui thi woh jigaree dost ban gaya hai"
  41,35,"yeh sift naseeb nahi hoti magar unn logon ko jo sabr karte hain, aur yeh maqam haasil nahi hota magar unn logon ko jo barray naseebay walay hain"
  41,36,"aur agar tum shetan ki taraf se koi aksaht mehsoos karo to Allah ki panah maang lau, woh sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
  41,37,Allah ki nshanyon mein se hain yeh raat aur din aur Sooraj aur chaand Sooraj aur chaand ko sajda nah karo balkay uss khuda ko sajda karo jis ne inhen peda kya hai agar fi al waqea tum usi ki ibadat karne walay ho
  41,38,"lekin agar yeh log ghuroor mein aa kar apni hi baat par uray rahen to parwa nahi, jo farishtay tairay rab ke Maqarrab hain woh shab o roz is ki tasbeeh kar rahay hain aur kabhi nahi thkte"
  41,39,"aur Allah ki nshanyon mein se aik yeh hai ke tum dekhte ho zameen sooni pari hui hai, phir jounhi ke hum ne is par pani barsaya, yakayak woh پھبک uthti hai aur phool jati hai yaqeenan jo khuda is meri hui zameen ko jala uthata hai woh mُrdon ko bhi zindagi bakhsnay wala hai yaqeenan woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  41,40,"jo log hamari ayaat ko ultay maienay p_hnate hain woh hum se kuch chupay hue nahi hain khud hi soch lau ke aaya woh shakhs behtar hai jo aag mein jhaunka jaane wala hai ya woh jo qayamat ke roz aman ki haalat mein haazir ho ga? karte raho jo kuch tum chaho, tumhari saari harkato ko Allah dekh raha hai"
  41,41,yeh woh log hain jin ke samnay kalaam nasiyaat aaya to unhon ne usay maan-ne se inkaar kar diya magar haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh aik zabardast kitaab hai
  41,42,"baatil nah samnay se is par aa sakta hai nah peechay se, yeh aik hakeem o hammeed ki nazil kardah cheez hai"
  41,43,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum se jo kuch kaha ja raha hai is mein koi cheez bhi aisi nahi hai jo tum se pehlay guzray hue Rasolo-n se nah kahi ja chuki ho be shak tumhara rab bara dar guzar karne wala hai, aur is ke sath barri dard naak saza dainay wala bhi hai"
  41,44,"agar hum iss ko ajmi quran bana kar bhaijtay to yeh log kehte"" kyun nah is ki ayaat khol kar bayan ki gayeen? kya ajeeb baat hai ke kalaam ajmi hai aur mukhatib arabi"" inn se kaho yeh quran imaan laane walon ke liye to hadaayat aur Shifa hai, magar jo log imaan nahi laatay unn ke liye yeh kaanon ki dot aur aankhon ki patti hai unn ka haal to aisa hai jaisay unn ko daur se puraka ja raha ho"
  41,45,iss se pehlay hum ne moose ko kitaab di thi aur is ke muamlay mein bhi yahi ikhtilaaf howa tha agar tairay rab ne pehlay hi aik baat tey nah kar di hoti to un ikhtilaaf karne walon ke darmain faisla chuka diya jata aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh log uss ki taraf se sakht iztiraab angaiz shak mein parre hue hain
  41,46,"jo koi naik amal kere ga apne hi liye acha kere ga, jo badi kere ga is ka wabaal usi par hoga, aur tera rab apne bundon ke haq mein zalim nahi hai"
  41,47,"uss saa-at ka ilm Allah hi ki taraf Rajay hota hai, wohi unn saaray phalon ko jaanta hai jo apne shagoofon mein se nikaltay hain, isi ko maloom hai ke konsi madah haamla hui hai aur kis ne bacha jina hai phir jis roz woh inn logon ko pukare ga ke kahan hain mere woh shareek? yeh kahin ge,"" hum arz kar chuke hain, aaj hum mein se koi iss ki gawahi dainay wala nahi hai """
  41,48,"uss waqt woh saaray mabood inn se gum ho jayen ge jinhein yeh is se pehlay pkarte thay, aur yeh log samajh len ge ke inn ke liye ab koi jaye panah nahi hai"
  41,49,"ensaan kabhi bhalai ki dua mangte nahi thakta, aur jab koi aafat iss par aa jati hai to mayoos o dil shakista ho jata hai"
  41,50,"magar jo n hi ke sakht waqt guzar jaane ke baad hum isay apni rehmat ka maza chukhatayhain, yeh kehta hai ke"" mein isi ka mustahiq hon, aur mein nahi samjhta ke qayamat kabhi aeye gi, lekin agar waqai mein apne Rab ki taraf pultya ا gaya to wahan bhi mazay karoon ga"" halaank kufar karne walon ko laziman hum bta kar rahen ge ke woh kya kar ke aeye hain aur inhen hum barray ganday azaab ka maza chkhayin ge"
  41,51,ensaan ko jab hum Nemat dete hain to woh mun pherte hai aur akarr jata hai aur jab usay koi aafat chhoo jati hai to lambi chorrie duayen karne lagta hai
  41,52,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho, kabhi tum ne yeh bhi socha ke agar waqai yeh quran khuda hi ki taraf se howa aur tum iss ka inkaar karte rahay to uss shakhs se barh kar bhatka howa aur kon hoga jo iss ki mukhalfat mein daur taq nikal gaya ho ?"
  41,53,anqareeb hum inn ko apni nishanain Afaq mein bhi deikhein ge aur un ke apne nafs mein bhi yahan taq ke inn par yeh baat khil jaye gi ke yeh quran waqai brhq hai kya yeh baat kaafi nahi hai ke tera rab har cheez ka Shahid hai ?
  41,54,"aagah raho, yeh log apne rab ki mulaqaat mein shak rakhtay hain sun rakho, woh har cheez par muheet hai"
